smart toilet
    Reasons
    1. Strong perfum smell
    2. Dirty toiled seat
    3. Dirty floor
    4. Dirty toiled
    5. Strong stink
    6. Toiled seat always up

    Flow
    1. WC is empty and closed, YAY images and info on door's screen
    2. Ultrasonic sensor detects possible user
    3. Camera detects face and take picture which is shown on screen
    4. Face recognition detects user as known user or new user
    5. New user gets presented with accept terms while opening door
    6. Photo is taken inside the empty toiled with current state
    7. As door opens, ambient music from deezer is playing
    8. In the toiled air quality sensor detects when to spray perfum
    9. Water sensor detects if there is pee on seat
    10. Ultrasonic sensor detects if user washed hands
    11. After user leaves the toiled photo is taken with current state
    12. Toiled seat is set back down
    13. After every session evaluation of usage is generated for this user
    14. User information might show on door screen, with dirtyness rank

